        RATIONS_WE_HAVE_MORE_THAN_ENOUGH_BUT_THE                             = 10173,  -- Rations? We have more than enough. But the drink...these hooligans guzzle it down like it was water. We're always low on supply!
        AH_YOU_CAME_AT_THE_PERFECT_TIME_YOU                                  = 10174,  -- Ah, you came at the perfect time. You're one of those adventurers, aren't you? Well, I need you to run an errand for me in the Yhoator Jungle.
        DEEP_IN_THAT_JUNGLE_THE_WILD_OPO_OPOS                                = 10175,  -- Deep in that jungle, the wild Opo-opos brew a special drink by fermenting berries in the trees.
        YOU_MUST_BE_WONDERING_HOW_YOU_GET_THERE                              = 10176,  -- You must be wondering how you get there, right? You'll find the Yhoator Jungle just beyond the Yuhtunga Jungle. But you should watch your back. There are a lot of wild animals creeping around in that place.
