        WILL_YOU_HELP_ME_OUT_OF_COURSE_MAYBE                                 = 10178,  -- Will you help me out? Of course. Maybe some other time.
        I_CAN_T_THANK_YOU_ENOUGH_NOW_TAKE                                    = 10179,  -- I can't thank you enough! Now take this % and fill it chock full of that Opo-Opo brew. I'll be waiting!
        WELL_I_GUESS_YOU_ADVENTURERS_MUST_BE_BUSY                            = 10180,  -- Well, I guess you adventurers must be busy with your adventuring. I'll try to find somebody else to go.
        OH_HAVE_YOU_CHANGED_YOUR_MIND                                        = 10181,  -- Oh, have you changed your mind?
        OKAY_NOW_LISTEN_UP_THE_OPO_OPOS_DON                                  = 10182,  -- Okay, now listen up. The Opo-opos don't hide their brew in the Yuhtunga Jungle, only in the Yhoator Jungle.
        WHEN_YOU_FIND_ONE_OF_THE_TREES_THOSE                                 = 10183,  -- When you find one of the trees those little buggers are making it in, fill this % up to the brim, and bring it back to me.
        MMM_MMM_THE_COLOR_THE_AROMA_ONLY_NATURE                              = 10184,  -- Mmm-mmm! The color! The aroma! Only nature can work magic like this!
        NOW_IF_ONLY_THOSE_HOOLIGANS_WOULD_APPRECIATE_IT                      = 10185,  -- Now if only those hooligans would appreciate it! Knowing them, this batch will be gone by the end of the night...
        HERE_S_A_LITTLE_SOMETHING_FOR_YOUR_TROUBLE                           = 10186,  -- Here's a little something for your trouble. Now, I have to remember to double our next order from our suppliers...
        OH_THANKS_AGAIN_FOR_HELPING_ME_OUT_WHAT                              = 10187,  -- Oh, thanks again for helping me out. What's beyond this door? Why, that's the kitchen--the heart of Norg. I can't let you in there, you know.
        MY_NAME_IS_JAUCRIBAIX_AND_I_AM_THE                                   = 10188,  -- My name is Jaucribaix, and I am the blacksmith here in Norg. I don't waste my time with that crystal synthesis rubbish. I forge all my katana in the traditional manner.
