        TO_LEARN_OF_WHERE_YOU_MAY_COME_ACROSS_2                              = 10199,  -- To learn of where you may come across the items I wish you to bring me, ask my pupils.
        TELL_THEM_I_SENT_YOU_AND_THEY_WILL_2                                 = 10200,  -- Tell them I sent you, and they will assist you with your preparations for the journey. Also, if you come across any trouble, you may ask them for further aid. However, I doubt you will require it.
