        YER_ADVENTURES_HAVE_ALREADY_TRAINED_YOU_T_BECOME                     = 10216,  -- Yer adventures have already trained you t'become a samurai. Now all that's left is for ya t'pledge your faith t'this blade. Yer power within will do the rest.
        RID_YERSELF_OF_ALL_UNNECESSARY_THOUGHTS_AND_FEEL                     = 10217,  -- Rid yerself of all unnecessary thoughts and feel the world around ya. Make yer soul an unclouded mirror...a motionless pond. Project yerself into yer blade. This be the legendary skill used by the samurai--Meikyo Shisui.
