        BEYOND_THE_MERIPHATAUD_MOUNTAINS_IS_AN_ANCIENT_FOREST                = 10225,  -- Beyond the Meriphataud Mountains is an ancient forest known as the Sanctuary of Zi'Tah. There you will find a tree that has been standing for over a thousand years.
