        VI_IISS5P_I_P_HI_5H_LG2W_9NAHL                                       = 10383,  -- Vi#Iiss5p%I%p HI`5H" _%%LG2W= 9nAhL~XLb7"= 1tCumCIoA= _L`gD%A= B43j5e Ghi%
        ID_10384                                                             = 10384,  -- @@@@@@@%+@
        GET_OUTTA_MY_FACE                                                    = 10385,  -- Get outta my face...
        WHAT_ENSETSU_ASKED_YOU_TO_BRING_ME_THIS                              = 10386,  -- What? Ensetsu asked you to bring me this %?
        HASN_T_CHANGED_A_BIT_HAS_HE_ALWAYS                                   = 10387,  -- Hasn't changed a bit, has he? Always was a weak little worm. If I saw his face, I would smack him so hard...
        WELL_AT_LEAST_HE_S_FINALLY_LEARNED_THE                               = 10388,  -- Well, at least he's finally learned the value of this blade. Yomi can now rest in peace...
        OH_AND_LET_ME_TELL_YOU_I_M                                           = 10389,  -- Oh, and let me tell you. I'm not doing this for Ensetsu. I only care about Yomi's daughters...
        ARRRG_SO_YOU_RE_THE_LANDLUBBIN_ADVENTURER_THAT                       = 10390,  -- Arrrg, so you're the landlubbin' adventurer that they sent from Bastok.
        I_M_A_BUSY_MAN_SO_LET_S                                              = 10391,  -- I'm a busy man, so let's cut with the chitchat and get right down to business.
        LATELY_YOU_ADVENTURERS_ARE_MAKING_QUITE_A_KILLIN                     = 10392,  -- Lately, you adventurers are making quite a killin' on items, weapons, and the like. We knew that you were out there, but we didn't think you'd be givin' us this much competition.
        BUT_RATHER_THAN_GETTIN_IN_EACH_OTHER_S                               = 10393,  -- But rather than gettin' in each other's way, I thought that there might be a way we could work together. What I want ya t'do is give me an idea of what you adventurers are capable of.
        THERE_ARE_A_FEW_ITEMS_THAT_ME_MATEYS                                 = 10394,  -- There are a few items that me mateys couldn't acquire. I want ya t'go and get them.
        TRAVEL_TO_ONE_OF_THEM_MOLTEN_LAVA_FALLS                              = 10395,  -- Travel to one of them molten lava falls in Ifrit's Cauldron.
        IF_YOU_THROW_IN_A_MONSTER_WILL_APPEAR                                = 10396,  -- If you throw in %, a monster will appear. Bring back the % that the beast has on it.
        DO_YA_THINK_YOU_CAN_HANDLE_IT_YA                                     = 10397,  -- Do ya think you can handle it, ya landlubber?
        HAH_HAH_HAH_ME_LANDLUBBIN_ADVENTURER_BROUGHT_BACK                    = 10398,  -- Hah hah hah! Me landlubbin' adventurer brought back %. It looks like I need to find myself some new mateys! Hah hah hah!
        I_GUESS_THIS_MEANS_YOU_VE_COMPLETED_YOUR                             = 10399,  -- I guess this means you've completed your mission. Now let me write you somethin' you can take back to...
        THAT_WON_T_BE_NECESSARY_SIR                                          = 10400,  -- That won't be necessary, sir.
        ARRRG_WHY_IF_IT_AIN_T_LITTLE_AYAYA                                   = 10401,  -- Arrrg, why if it ain't little Ayaya. Ya get prettier every time I sees ya.
        GILGAMESH_IT_WAS_FINE_WHEN_YOU_CALLED_ME                             = 10402,  -- Gilgamesh. It was fine when you called me that when I was a child, but I'm twenty years old now.
        SO_WHAT_BRINGS_YA_T_THESE_HERE_PARTS                                 = 10403,  -- So, what brings ya t'these here parts? Come to check up on your adventurer?
        THAT_IS_ONE_OF_THE_REASONS_WE_WOULDN                                 = 10404,  -- That is one of the reasons. We wouldn't want you snatching up one of Bastok's best.
        IF_I_WANTED_TO_SNATCH_UP_BASTOK_S                                    = 10405,  -- If I wanted to snatch up Bastok's best, I'd be snatching up the fine samurai standing in front of me. How about it, Ayaya? Leave that boring job of yours and join us!
        WE_D_LOVE_T_HAVE_YOU_YOU_D                                           = 10406,  -- We'd love t'have you. You'd have the chance t'wield your blade whenever you please, not when that president says you can. Arrrg, what d'ya say?
        WHILE_I_AM_FLATTERED_BY_YOUR_OFFER_I                                 = 10407,  -- While I am flattered by your offer, I am satisfied with, and hold pride in, my current post.
        I_REALIZE_THAT_I_STILL_HAVE_MUCH_TO                                  = 10408,  -- I realize that I still have much to learn, but at the same time I feel that I must travel the roads I see fit to travel.
        SWORDS_AND_MUSKETS_ARE_NOT_MADE_TO_BE                                = 10409,  -- Swords and muskets are not made to be drawn. That is what my parents taught me, and those are the words I wish to live by.
        AYAYA                                                                = 10410,  -- Ayaya...
        I_HAVE_BROUGHT_WITH_ME_A_DOCUMENT_FROM                               = 10411,  -- I have brought with me a document from the president himself. It covers the treatment of Bastokan adventurers, as well as overseas trade guidelines.
        YOU_MAY_WANT_TO_READ_OVER_THE_DETAILS                                = 10412,  -- You may want to read over the details at a later time. You need not give an answer now. However, I trust that Norg will take steps in the right direction.
        ARRRG_YA_DON_T_LEAVE_MUCH_ROOM_FER                                   = 10413,  -- Arrrg, ya don't leave much room fer choice now, do you?
        I_LL_TAKE_THAT_AS_A_COMPLIMENT_I                                     = 10414,  -- I'll take that as a compliment. I learned everything I needed to know from the years I spent here in training.
        OKAY_OKAY_YOU_GO_BACK_AND_TELL_THE                                   = 10415,  -- Okay, okay. You go back and tell the old president I said hello. Oh, and don't ya forget t'talk to Ryoma before you leave. It's the least ya could do fer him.
        I_M_SORRY_BUT_THAT_WILL_HAVE_TO                                      = 10416,  -- I'm sorry, but that will have to wait until another day... However, maybe next time I will bring along my younger sister.
        YOUR_ASSIGNMENT_IN_NORG_IS_COMPLETE_YOU_MAY                          = 10417,  -- Your assignment in Norg is complete. You may return to Bastok now, and do not forget to report to Naji upon your arrival.
        WHO_THA_HELL_ARE_YOU_NEVER_HEARD_OF                                  = 10418,  -- Who tha hell are you? %? Never heard of ya. How am I supposed to remember the name of one puny ant when there's millions of ya swarmin' around?
        DO_A_LITTLE_WORK_AROUND_HERE_AND_THERE                               = 10419,  -- Do a little work around here, and there might be somebody that'll remember your ugly face...no guarantees, though.
        YA_GOTTA_GET_PEOPLE_T_TRUST_YA_ONCE                                  = 10420,  -- Ya gotta get people t'trust ya. Once people do, you'll start makin' a name fer yerself 'round here.
        I_MIGHTA_HEARDA_SOMEBODY_THAT_WENT_BY_THAT                           = 10421,  -- %? I mighta hearda somebody that went by that name, but I meets a lot of people in me line of work.
        DON_T_LOOK_SO_UPSET_THERE_MATEY_IT                                   = 10422,  -- Don't look so upset there, matey. It takes a lot t'get people t'remember ya. It all starts with trust!
        YER_AN_ADVENTURER_GO_AN_HELP_PEOPLE_OUT                              = 10423,  -- Yer an adventurer, go an' help people out. Little by little, they'll begin t'trust ya, but don't expect anythin' right away.
        WAIT_A_MINUTE_I_REMEMBER_YOU_MICH_NO                                 = 10424,  -- Wait a minute, I remember you...Mich...no...%, right?
        YA_SEE_DO_A_LITTLE_WORK_AND_PEOPLE                                   = 10425,  -- Ya see, do a little work, and people start recognizin' ya. Keep up tha good work!
        WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_HEAR_YER_NAME                                       = 10426,  -- Well, if it isn't %. Hear yer name lots 'round these parts lately. Why, I remembers when you was nothin' but a measly insect.
        THANKS_T_ME_ADVICE_YOU_RE_DOIN_QUITE                                 = 10427,  -- Thanks t'me advice, you're doin' quite well here in Norg.
        OH_I_WAS_JUST_TALKIN_TO_ME_MATEYS                                    = 10428,  -- Oh, %. I was just talkin' to me mateys about ya the other day.
        NOTHIN_BAD_OF_COURSE_THEY_HAD_ALL_HEARD                              = 10429,  -- Nothin' bad, of course. They had all heard about yer deeds fer Norg. Some are even startin' t'think that maybe all you adventurers ain't so bad after all.
        THERE_S_HARDLY_A_SOUL_IN_NORG_THAT                                   = 10430,  -- %! There's hardly a soul in Norg that doesn't know yer bloody name.
        OH_SORRY_BOUT_THAT_ME_MUM_NEVER_DID                                  = 10431,  -- Oh, sorry 'bout that. Me mum never did teach me no manners. I'll watch me damn mouth...I mean, I'll watch me mouth from now on.
        MISTER_MISS_YOU_VE_BECOME_QUITE_THE_HOUSEHOLD                        = 10432,  -- %...Mister/Miss] %. You've become quite the household name 'round Norg.
        ALL_ME_MATEYS_KEEP_ASKIN_ME_IF_I                                     = 10433,  -- All me mateys keep askin' me if I can introduce them to ya. You've made quite a reputation for yerself!
        LOOKIN_AT_YA_GETS_ME_THINKIN_LIKE_I                                  = 10434,  -- Lookin' at ya gets me thinkin' like I should leave tha life on the open sea, and become an adventurer!
        MISTER_MISS_THERE_S_ALREADY_RUMORS_OF_YER                            = 10435,  -- Mister/Miss] %! There's already rumors of yer last adventure goin' 'round Norg. You're startin' t'become some sorta legend!
        LORD_LADY_NEXT_T_OUR_LEADER_GILGAMESH_YER                            = 10436,  -- Lord/Lady] %! Next t'our leader, Gilgamesh, yer the most famous person in all'a Norg! Some of me mateys are even callin' ya a hero!
        MAY_THE_LIGHT_OF_THE_DAWN_GODDESS_SHINE                              = 10437,  -- May the light of the Dawn Goddess shine down upon ya in all yer journeys 'round Vana'diel!
        PRESS_THE_CONFIRMATION_BUTTON                                        = 10438,  -- Press the confirmation button.
        WHAT_SONG_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_1                                      = 10439,  -- What song do you want to hear? (1) Next Page. Field Battle (Solo). Field Battle (Party). Dungeon Battle (Solo). Dungeon Battle (Party). Windurst. San d'Oria. Bastok. Chateau d'Oraguille. Metalworks. Heavens Tower. Jeuno. Ru'Lude Gardens. Selbina. Mahura. Ronfaure. Sarutabaruta. Gustaberg. Batallia Downs. Sauromugue Champaign. Rolanberry Fields.
        WHAT_SONG_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_2                                      = 10440,  -- What song do you want to hear? (2) Next Page. Northlands. Delkfutt's Tower. Castle Zvahl. Shadow Lord Battle. Shadow Lord Theme. Bravery. Ghelsba. Ferry. Prelude. Mog House. Installation. Game Over, man! Airship. No Hope 1. No Hope 2. Anger. Sadness. Mid-Boss. Sometime, Somewhere. Memories. Uneasy. Theme (2). Theme (3).
        WHAT_SONG_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_3                                      = 10441,  -- What song do you want to hear? (3) First Page. 130. 131. 132. 133. 165. 166. 167. 168. 170. Music...stop!
        WHAT_SONG_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_4                                      = 10442,  -- What song do you want to hear? (4) Next Page. EX Field Battle! (Party). EX Dungeon Battle (Party). EX Mid-Boss. Eald'narche. Crystal Warriors. Raogrimm's Theme. To Tu'Lia! Athanasium. Grav'iton. Kam'lanaut's Theme. EX Ending. Quest Complete! Quest 1. Quest 2. Quest 3.
        WHAT_SONG_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_5                                      = 10443,  -- What song do you want to hear? (5) Previous Page. Yve'noile. Norg. Kazham. Rabao. Jungle Fever. Altepa. Tu'Lia. The Sanctuary of Zi'Tah. Ro'Maeve. The Hall of the Gods. Ve'Lugannon Palace. Chocobo de Go. Wedding Bells.
        OWZIE_WOWZIE_DON_T_MAKE_ME_TALK_I                                    = 10444,  -- Owzie-wowzie! Don't make me talk. I hurt all over!
        TRY_THOUGH_YOU_MAY_THERE_WILL_COME_A                                 = 10445,  -- Try though you may, there will come a time when failure is inevitable.
        CHANNEL_THAT_AGONY_AND_BITTERNESS_INTO_CREATING_A                    = 10446,  -- Channel that agony and bitterness into creating a new plan.
        OWZIE_WOWZIE_DON_T_MAKE_ME_TALK_I_2                                  = 10447,  -- Owzie-wowzie! Don't make me talk. I hurt all over!
        HEY_YOU_RE_THAT_FAMOUS_ADVENTURER                                    = 10448,  -- Hey! You're that famous adventurer, %!
        YIPPEE_THIS_IS_MY_LUCKY_DAY                                          = 10449,  -- Yippee! This is my lucky day!
        LET_ME_INTRODUCE_MYSELF_I_AM_FROM_THE                                = 10450,  -- Let me introduce myself. I am from the Rhinostery in Windurst. I do research on various living things.
        AND_I_M_THE_BESTY_WESTY_THEY_VE                                      = 10451,  -- And I'm the besty-westy they've got! I've been looking into phenomena at a certain place.
        WHAT_PHENOMENA_YOU_ASK_WELL_THERE_ARE_THESE                          = 10452,  -- What phenomena, you ask? Well, there are these giant crystals, you see! And from those crystals, a strangey-wangey power is constantly pouring forth...
        THESE_CRYSTALS_ARE_FOUND_ALL_OVER_VANA_DIEL                          = 10453,  -- These crystals are found all over Vana'diel, and their energies affect the surrounding ecosystems. Our research team had been investigating the unusual emanations when...
        GUESS_WHAT                                                           = 10454,  -- Guess what!
        WE_FINALLY_SUCCEEDED_IN_AWAKENING_THE_CRYSTALS                       = 10455,  -- We finally succeeded in awakening the crystals!
        OUR_THEORY_ON_WHAT_LAY_DORMANT_INSIDE_THE                            = 10456,  -- Our theory on what lay dormant inside the crystals was proven to be rightaru on the money! Except they didn't appreciate being woken up... We were attacked... We were bested-wested...
        WHY_DO_THEY_SO_DESPISE_TALKING_WITH_US                               = 10457,  -- Why do they so despise talking with us that they would rather fight? And what on Vana'diel would happen if someone were to defeat them?
        I_BET_YOU_COULD_DO_IT_YOU_CALL                                       = 10458,  -- I bet you could do it! You call yourself an adventurer, right? Give it a shot!
        TAKE_UP_THE_CHALLENGE_BRING_IT_ON_AH                                 = 10459,  -- Take up the challenge? Bring it on! Ah, no, thanks...
        GREAT_HERE_TAKE_THIS_BUT_BE_WARNED_ONLY                              = 10460,  -- Great! Here, take this %. But be warned--only a person who carries one can enter the crystal.
        THIS_WILL_AWAKEN_THE_GIANT_CRYSTAL_THAT_IS                           = 10461,  -- This % will awaken the giant crystal that is found [in Ifrit's Cauldron/in the Quicksand Caves/in the Den of Rancor/in Cape Teriggan/in Fei'Yin/in The Boyahda Tree].
        WITHOUT_IT_YOU_WON_T_BE_GETTING_INSIDE                               = 10462,  -- Without it, you won't be getting inside no matter how sneaky-weaky you are! Oh, and if you want to take some friends with you, they also have to get % from me. Okey-dokey?
        IF_YOU_DON_T_PREPARE_YOURSELF_FOR_BATTLE                             = 10463,  -- If you don't prepare yourself for battle, you'll get beaten to a pulp, like we did!
        AS_SOON_AS_WE_GATHER_OUR_COMPANIONS_WE                               = 10464,  -- As soon as we gather our companions, we'll be jumping into the fray again. I just hope this little researcher doesn't get in our way...
        WHAT_NONSENSE_IF_I_DON_T_GO_WITH                                     = 10465,  -- What nonsense! If I don't go with you, there's no pointaru to the research now, is there?
        HOW_D_IT_GO_WOWY_WOW_WOW_YOU                                         = 10466,  -- How'd it go!? Wowy-wow-wow! You defeated a prime avatar!
        I_SEE_THE_PRIME_AVATAR_SAID_THAT_TO                                  = 10467,  -- ...I see. The prime avatar said that to you? I wonder what it could mean.
        THERE_IS_NO_NEED_TO_UNDERSTAND_YOU_WILL                              = 10468,  -- ...There is no need to understand... ...You will forget what I have said...
        Y_YOU_YOU_RE                                                         = 10469,  -- Y-you, you're...!
        YOU_HAVE_POWER                                                       = 10470,  -- ...You have power...
        WILL_YOU_ALLOW_THAT_POWER_TO_SLUMBER_FOR                             = 10471,  -- ...Will you allow...that power... ...to slumber...for eternity...?
        SURRENDER_THAT_POWER_TO_ME_AND_I_WILL                                = 10472,  -- Surrender...that power...to me... and I...will craft...that power... into whatever...you desire...
        WE_MEET_AGAIN                                                        = 10473,  -- ...We meet...again...
        MY_CHARGE_MUST_BE_FULFILLED                                          = 10474,  -- ...My charge...must...be...fulfilled...
        THE_BEAST_WILL_CLAIM_ITS_DUE                                         = 10475,  -- The beast...will claim...its due...
        CHOOSE_WHAT_DO_YOU_DESIRE_WHAT_DO_YOU                                = 10476,  -- Choose... What...do you desire...? What...do you seek?
        WHAT_DO_YOU_DESIRE_GIL_NOTHING_A_PACT                                = 10477,  -- What do you desire? %. %. %. %. Gil. Nothing (a pact with the avatar).
        THIS_IS_WHAT_YOU_DESIRE                                              = 10478,  -- ...This is what you desire...?
        YOU_WANT_YES_WAIT                                                    = 10479,  -- You want %? Yes. Wait!
        YOU_WANT_YES_WAIT_2                                                  = 10480,  -- You want %? Yes. Wait!
        YOU_WANT_YES_WAIT_3                                                  = 10481,  -- You want %? Yes. Wait!
        YOU_WANT_YES_WAIT_4                                                  = 10482,  -- You want %? Yes. Wait!
        GIL_IS_WHAT_YOU_TRULY_WANT_YES_WAIT                                  = 10483,  -- Gil is what you truly want? Yes. Wait!
        ARE_YOU_SURE_YES_WAIT                                                = 10484,  -- Are you sure? Yes. Wait!
        LISTEN_TO_THE_VOICE_WITHOUT_MY_VOICE_WITH                            = 10485,  -- Listen...to the voice without--my voice--with your ears...and your heart...
        BRING_ME_POWER_HIGHER_DEEPER_STRONGER                                = 10486,  -- Bring me... Power... Higher... Deeper... ...... Stronger...
        SOMETHING_INTERFERING                                                = 10487,  -- ...? ...something...interfering...?
        LISTEN_TO_THE_VOICE_WITHIN_YOU                                       = 10488,  -- %...! Listen to the voice within you!
        IF_YOU_FOCUS_YOU_WILL_SEE_THE_TRUE                                   = 10489,  -- If you focus, you will see the true Vana'diel!
        EVEN_IF_THAT                                                         = 10490,  -- ...Even if...that...
        UH_HUH_I_WENT_ALL_SPACEY_WACEY_FOR                                   = 10491,  -- Uh? Huh? I went all spacey-wacey for a moment there...
        UM_WHO_WERE_YOU_AGAIN_WAS_I_SPEAKING                                 = 10492,  -- Um, who were you again? Was I speaking with you? What were we talking about?
        DID_I_TELL_YOU_I_M_A_RESEARCHER                                      = 10493,  -- Did I tell you I'm a researcher from the Rhinostery in Windurst already?
        YOU_ARE_NOW_ABLE_TO_SUMMON                                           = 10494,  -- You are now able to summon [Ifrit/Titan/Leviathan/Garuda/Shiva/Ramuh].
        HUH_WHAT_DO_I_KNOW_WHERE_ILDY_GOLDY                                  = 10495,  -- Huh? What? Do I know where Ildy-Goldy is?
        YEAH_YOU_JUSTARU_MISSED_HIM_HE_WENT_OFF                              = 10496,  -- Yeah, you justaru missed him. He went off towards Cape Terrrigan with the improved tuning fork of air.
        ILDY_GOLDY_WILL_WIPE_THE_FLOOR_WITH_THAT                             = 10497,  -- Ildy-Goldy will wipe the floor with that avatar. I wonder what kind of research data he'll bring back for us?
        HM_DID_HE_SEEM_A_LITTLE_DIFFERENT_FROM                               = 10498,  -- Hm? Did he seem a little different from usual?
        WELL_NOW_THAT_YOU_MENTION_IT_HE_DID                                  = 10499,  -- Well, now that you mention it, he did ask me to give this to any adventurers that came looking for him...
        I_GUESS_THAT_MUST_MEAN_YOU_HERE_YOU                                  = 10500,  -- I guess that must mean you. Here you go. Seems like a clear invitation to go take on the avatar in Cape Teriggan yourself.
        I_VE_GIVEN_YOU_WHAT_ILDY_GOLDY_HAD                                   = 10501,  -- I've given you what Ildy-Goldy had me hold on to. You should be on your way to Cape Teriggan.
        HM_YOU_RE_GOING_TO_HELP_OUT_ILDY                                     = 10502,  -- ...Hm? You're going to help out Ildy-Goldy, but first you want to take on the avatar in Cape Teriggan under your own steam?
        CHECK_IT_OUT_YOURSELF_I_LIKE_TO_DO                                   = 10503,  -- Check it out yourself? I like to do things my way... All on my lonesome...?
        YOU_GOT_GUTS_KID_WELL_EITHER_WAY_IS                                  = 10504,  -- ...You got guts, kid. Well, either way is fine with me.
        WHAT_YOU_LOST_THE                                                    = 10505,  -- What!? You lost the %!?
        WHAT_KIND_OF_AN_ADVENTURER_ARE_YOU_WELL                              = 10506,  -- What kind of an adventurer are you...? Well, don't go losing this one, okay?
        WE_M_M_MEET_AGAIN_THERE_IS_NO                                        = 10507,  -- ...We m-m-meet again... ...There is no need for violence, adventurer...
        I_JUST_WISH_TO_ASK_YOU_SOM_M                                         = 10508,  -- ...I just wish to ask you som-m-me questions. ...Why do you think the avatars...give power to people...without a reason...?
        AND_HAVE_YOU_FELT_THE_POWER_OF_THE                                   = 10509,  -- ..And...have you...felt the power...of the avatars...?
        HAHAHA_RATHER_THAN_STRENGTH_WITHOUT_PURPOSE_YOU_SHOULD               = 10510,  -- Hahaha... ...Rather than strength without purpose... ...you should be seeking...true power...
        WE_M_M_MEET_AGAIN_I_MUST_FULFILL                                     = 10511,  -- We m-m-meet...again... I must...fulfill...my charge.
        YOU_MUST_SEEK_POWER                                                  = 10512,  -- You must...seek power...
        AND_I_SHALL_C_C_CLAIM_MY_DUE                                         = 10513,  -- ...And I...shall c-c-claim...my due...
        WHAT_YOU_WANT_ANOTHER                                                = 10514,  -- What? You want another %?
        OH_ALL_RIGHT_BUT_BE_CAREFUL_WAREFUL_WITH                             = 10515,  -- Oh, all right... But be careful-wareful with this one! These things don't grow on star trees, you know.
        HMMM_HRMMM_SO_IT_S_TIME_TO_USE                                       = 10516,  -- Hmmm... Hrmmm... So it's time to use...no...
        HELLO_YOU_RE_AN_ADVENTURER_RIGHT_MAYBE_YOU                           = 10517,  -- Hello? You're an adventurer, right? Maybe you can help us out.
        LET_ME_INTRODUCE_MYSELF_AND_MY_COMPANION_WE                          = 10518,  -- Let me introduce myself and my companion. We're from the Rhinostery in Windurst.
        I_WAS_HIRED_BY_THE_MINISTRY_TO_ACCOMPANY                             = 10519,  -- I was hired by the ministry to accompany this researcher to [Ifrit's Cauldron/the Quicksand Caves/the Den of Rancor/Cape Teriggan/Fei'Yin/the Boyahda Tree] and assist him in his study of a series of giant crystals.
        BUT_WHAT_WAS_WAITING_FOR_US_INSIDE_THOSE                             = 10520,  -- But what was waiting for us inside those crystals was more than I could deal with...
        WE_TRIED_COUNTLESS_TIMES_BUT_I_COULD_NOT                             = 10521,  -- We tried countless times, but I could not defeat that beast. Another researcher at the Rhinostery sympathized with our plight and developed an improved tuning fork.
        NO_NO_NO_NO_NO_THAT_CRAZY_WAZY                                       = 10522,  -- No no no no no! That crazy-wazy contraption won't provide us with any useful data!
