        YOU_KNOW_THAT_YOU_PROBABLY_WON_T_GAIN                                = 10532,  -- You know that you probably won't gain anything from this battle-waddle. Are you sure you still want the fork?
        ARE_YOU_REALLY_DILLY_SURE_FORK_ME_ON                                 = 10533,  -- Are you really-dilly sure? Fork me! On second thought...
