        I_DON_T_THINK_YOU_LL_GET_MUCH                                        = 10552,  -- I don't think you'll get much out of it, but if you want to go get your buttaru kicked by the prime avatar again, all you have to do is ring another % near a giant crystal.
        REMEMBER_THAT_YOU_MUST_FIGHT_THE_PRIME_AVATAR                        = 10553,  -- Remember that you must fight the prime avatar as a level # summoner. As you already know, this will not be an easy task. Prepare well for the battle.
