        BUT_IT_STILL_LOOKS_A_HELLUVA_LOT_LIKE                                = 10627,  -- But it still looks a helluva lot like the work of the greatest pirate inventor that ever lived--Mitsunari the Poisonclaw.
        BUT_HE_LEFT_NORG_OVER_TWENTY_YEARS_AGO                               = 10628,  -- But he left Norg over twenty years ago, and is assumed dead and gone. There have been stories of a pupil of his, but...
        ARGH_BUT_WHAT_DO_I_KNOW_THE_ONLY                                     = 10629,  -- Argh! But what do I know!? The only person that has anything close to a lead is that weasel, Ensetsu. Go to his house in Bastok and make him tell us all he knows.
        YOU_RE_JUST_THE_PERSON_I_WAS_LOOKING                                 = 10630,  -- You're just the person I was looking for. We've got our hands on some new info regarding Mitsunari's treasure.
        IT_LOOKS_LIKE_A_PACK_OF_THOSE_SLIMY                                  = 10631,  -- It looks like a pack of those slimy Sahagins stole the Poisonclaw's % when our men were transporting it.
        FOR_THE_PAST_FEW_DAYS_WE_VE_BEEN                                     = 10632,  -- For the past few days we've been combing the Sea Serpent Grotto, but it's beginning to look like the beasts aren't hiding it anywhere near Norg.
        BUT_THE_FISH_FACED_FIENDS_ARE_ONLY_BEASTMEN                          = 10633,  -- But the fish-faced fiends are only beastmen, so you wouldn't think they could take it off Elshimo Island. It's gotta be somewhere close.
