        I_CAN_SENSE_YOUR_SKILLS_HAVE_IMPROVED_MUCH                           = 10806,  -- %, I can sense your skills have improved much since you first wielded the mumeito I forged for you many moons ago. However, you still have many malms to travel on the road to mastery of the great katana. Do you feel you have what it takes to complete your journey?
